00:45:42,160 --> 00:45:52,600
It is like something I care about so much and which pissed me off so much when you had, like, all these billionaires, you know, including the one that runs X being like, oh, Taylor Lorenz, blah, blah, blah.

535
00:45:52,680 --> 00:45:57,320
It's like, you can say a lot of things about me, but free speech is like an issue that I would die for.

536
00:45:57,520 --> 00:45:59,520
It's like the only reason I like America.

